12:25.570 --> 12:27.703
And when he finally had enough
strength to fly on his own,

12:27.705 --> 12:29.488
I opened up that box
and set him free.

12:29.490 --> 12:30.790
No kidding.
It was one

12:30.792 --> 12:32.908
of the most beautiful things
I had ever seen.

12:32.910 --> 12:35.211
