in the entire Milky Way.

14:02.616 --> 14:04.450
Speaking of which, do you like
Snickers or Milky Way?

14:04.452 --> 14:05.885
I like Three Musketeers.

14:07.087 --> 14:09.088
Even though I don't know
what nougat is.

14:13.226 --> 14:14.165
Hey, what you doing?

14:14.190 --> 14:15.771
