14:29.510 --> 14:31.360
Yeah, really cool.

14:31.362 --> 14:33.579
All right. See you later, Dad.

14:33.581 --> 14:35.748
And Dad.

14:37.650 --> 14:40.119
You know, if they have kids,
we'd be their grandpappies.

14:40.121 --> 14:42.321
Ow!

14:45.092 --> 14:46.492
Well, to make
a long story short,

14:46.494 --> 14:48.210
