gonna shut up now,

15:18.626 --> 15:19.742
'cause you're
a really good kisser,

15:19.744 --> 15:21.160
and the last thing
I want to do is...

15:27.335 --> 15:29.468
Look at you
making breakfast.

15:29.470 --> 15:30.753
It's what the army
trains you to do

15:30.755 --> 15:33.139
