17:23.251 --> 17:24.532
always putting his career
ahead of me.

17:24.535 --> 17:25.701
He's a doctor.

17:25.703 --> 17:27.836
Well, not a real doctor,
a glass doctor.

17:27.838 --> 17:29.655
You know, like if you get
a crack in your windshield,

17:29.657 --> 17:31.257
