19:08.654 --> 19:10.487
Knowing what you know now,

19:10.489 --> 19:12.406
and feeling how you feel now,

19:12.408 --> 19:14.658
would you have done anything
differently?

19:15.493 --> 19:16.777
No.

19:16.779 --> 19:19.613
I just would've done it
a few more times.

19:20.448 --> 19:22.699
There you go.

19:22.701 --> 19:24.952
That's what
love's all about.

